MFashion E-Commerce Website

Welcome to MFashion E-Commerce, your go-to platform for the latest fashion trends, stylish apparel, and accessories. This website provides a seamless shopping experience with a modern design and intuitive user interface.

🚀 Live Website

MFashion E-Commerc : https://mfashionecom.netlify.app/

📌 Features

🛍️ Product Catalog – Browse through a wide range of fashion products.

🔍 Search & Filter – Easily find products based on categories, price range, and more.

🛒 Shopping Cart – Add products to the cart and manage your purchases.

💳 Secure Checkout – Seamless checkout process with multiple payment options.

👤 User Authentication – Register, login, and manage your profile.

⭐ Customer Reviews – View and add reviews for products.

📱 Responsive Design – Fully optimized for mobile, tablet, and desktop.

🏗️ Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Hosting: Netlify

📦 Installation & Setup

If you want to run the project locally, follow these steps:

Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/ARYAN1125/E-Commerce.git

Navigate to the project folder

cd mfashion-ecom

Open the project
Simply open the index.html file in your browser.

